  <string name="app_info">
    <![CDATA[
    <h1>Antigravity!</h1>
    <p>
      Antigravity is a file manager for <a href="https://app.net">App.net</a>.
      It is <a href="http://floatboth.com">a&nbsp;{&nbsp;float:&nbsp;both&nbsp;}&nbsp;production</a>.
      Follow <a href="https://app.net/myfreeweb">@myfreeweb</a> on App.net :-)
    </p>
    <h2>Why the name?</h2>
    <p>
      Well, I made Antigravity in response to <a href="http://orbitapp.net/">Orbit</a>, a similar app for iOS and OS X.
      Also <a href="http://xkcd.com/353/">an xkcd reference</a>, obviously.
    </p>
